org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601

Class FullCornerLatitude

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.UasDatalinkLatitude
      • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.FullCornerLatitude
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, IUasDatalinkValue

    public class FullCornerLatitude
extends UasDatalinkLatitude
    Corner Latitude Point (ST 0601 Items 82/84/86/88).

    From ST:

    Frame latitude for image corner. Full Range. Based on WGS84 ellipsoid.

    Map -(2^31-1)..(2^31-1) to +/-90. Use -(2^31) as an "error" indicator. -(2^31) = 0x80000000.

    Resolution: ~42 nano degrees.
